# Outlook Excel Value Updater

This Python script automates a common workflow using Outlook and Excel.

It:

- Searches for a specific Outlook email based on sender and subject
- Locates the attachment with a date-based filename (e.g. `123_ABC_YYYYMMDD`)
- Extracts a value (USD) from cell A1 of the attachment
- Inserts the next business day and that value into a master Excel sheet
- Prepares an Outlook email with the updated file ready to send

